title: MaiPage
text:
Welcome to Mai Webpage!
I am a 4th-year Environmental Studies Major at St. Olaf College in southern Minnesota. I also study Statistics and Data Science as well as Race and Ethnic Studies.
Click the 3 lines on the top left of the page to access more information about me and 2 projects from my Data Science class!!
See below to connect with me and more information about the construction of this website.
Don’t like the theme? Click the switch on the section to the right of the website title and three lines.
